text: Volnovakha () is a small city in the Donetsk Oblast of Ukraine. It is the administrative center of Volnovakha Raion, one of the 18 districts of the Donetsk Oblast. ==Other websites== * Site of town * Official site of Volnovaha raiderzhadministration * Official site of Volnovaha town Council Category:Cities in Donetsk Oblast
